headline: Latest News In AI Chips - Advancing XR: Qualcomm and VoxelSensors Join Forces
summary: VoxelSensors has announced a collaboration with Qualcomm Technologies to optimize its Single Photon Active Event Sensor (SPAES™) 3D sensing technology for use with Snapdragon XR Platforms. This partnership aims to address critical challenges in depth sensing technology by providing 10x power savings and lower latency, which enhances the performance of XR applications under varied lighting conditions.
